div.div: On the day of his wedding, he was swept out by his wife and returned to his residence, but was madly asked for a kiss by a glamorous stranger. The moment he touched his lips, he felt a torrent of water surge into his body. When he woke up again, There are more than ten thousand strangers' memories in my mind... (Source: AC.QQ, translated)

A strange relationship began when orphan siblings met a old woman who claimed to be their grandmother, but this old woman is the superior master of Murim, who has lost her memory due to a disease. The woman recognized the hidden talent of the eldest sibling and started to train him, thus began the journey of Jinmu Sin-Mo, the last disciple.
The boy is destined to reach the end of sky!
(Source: Kakao, translated and edited)
